
component:
Atlas: Cloud version, DB will be on cloud
Mongo
MongoD: Mongo Daemon or mongo server that will host the DB.
Compass: It is a GUI equivalent to workbench of MySql , Sql developer of SQL


show dbs  => display the db list

create database
cmd:   use <database_name>
create and move inside db or if db exists then move inside the db
example: use seed

drop the database
cmd: db.dropDatabase();

To check the db name
cmd: db

create collection(table) employees
cmd:  db.createCollection('employees')


display the list of collections:
cmd:  show collections



drop the collection
cmd: db.<collection_name>/drop()


create db -> use db_name
